<i>noun</i>: 학군단 [학꾼단] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>학군단 [학꾼단]</dt><br>
<dd>ROTC; Reserve Officers' Training Corps</dd><br>
<dd>복무를 지원한 대학생에게 군사 교육과 훈련을 실시하여 졸업 후 장교로 임명하는 군사 교육단.</dd><br>
<dd>A training corps for providing military training and drills to college students who have applied for service in the army, and then appointing those students as commissioned officers after their graduation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>